subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: The new No. 1 women’s player, Jelena Jankovic, won her second title in two weeks, defeating Nadia Petrova of Russia, 6-4, 6-3, on Sunday in the final of the Porsche Grand Prix in Stuttgart, Germany.
